'''黃河巨龍'''（[[學名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Huanghetitan''}}，意為「[[黃河|黃河]]的巨人」）是一[[屬|屬]][[蜥腳下目|蜥腳下目]][[恐龍|恐龍]]，屬於基礎[[巨龍形類|巨龍形類]]，化石發現於[[中國|中國]][[甘肅省|甘肅省]]的[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]早期地層。

==物種==
[[File:Huanghetitan_ruyangensis.jpg|thumb]]
[[模式種|模式種]]'''劉家峽黃河巨龍'''（''H. liujiaxiaensis''）於2006年由尤海魯等人所敘述、命名，所知來自零碎的化石，包含兩節尾椎、幾乎完整的[[薦骨|薦骨]]、[[肋骨|肋骨]]碎片以及左[[肩胛骨|肩胛骨]]，是在2004年發現於甘肅省蘭州盆地東部的{{link-en|河口群|Hekou Group}}。<ref name="youetal2006">{{Cite journal|author=You, H., Li, D., Zhou, L., and Ji, Q.|year=2006|title=''Huanghetitan liujiaxiaensis''. a New Sauropod Dinosaur from the Lower Cretaceous Hekou Group of Lanzhou Basin, Gansu Province, China|journal=Geological Review|volume=52|issue=5|pages=668-674}}</ref>

第二個種'''汝陽黃河巨龍'''（''H. ruyangensis''）是在[[河南省|河南省]][[汝陽縣|汝陽縣]]的{{link-en|郝岭組|Haoling Formation}}發現，並於2007年由[[呂君昌|呂君昌]]等人敘述、命名。<ref name="luetal2007">{{Cite journal|author=Lu J., Xu, L., Zhang, X., Hu, W., Wu, Y., Jia, S., and Ji, Q.|year=2007|title=A new gigantic sauropod dinosaur with the deepest known body cavity from the Cretaceous of Asia|journal=Acta Geologica Sinica|volume=81|pages=167-176}}</ref>近期的分類研究發現此物種可能與劉家峽黃河巨龍沒有關連，甚至需要建立新的屬。<ref name="mannionetal">{{cite journal|doi=10.1111/zoj.12029|title=Osteology of the Late Jurassic Portuguese sauropod dinosaur ''Lusotitan atalaiensis'' (Macronaria) and the evolutionary history of basal titanosauriforms|journal=Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society|volume=168|pages=98–206|year=2013|last1=Mannion|first1=Philip D.|last2=Upchurch|first2=Paul|last3=Barnes|first3=Rosie N.|last4=Mateus|first4=Octávio|url=http://docentes.fct.unl.pt/sites/default/files/omateus/files/mannion_et_al_2013_sauropod_lusotitan_portugal.pdf|access-date=2020-10-03|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209202332/https://docentes.fct.unl.pt/sites/default/files/omateus/files/mannion_et_al_2013_sauropod_lusotitan_portugal.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==體型==
[[File:"Huanghetitan"_ruyangensis_Scale.svg|thumb]]
汝楊黃河巨龍的化石只有部份脊椎及幾根肋骨，最長的達3公尺，使其成為已知最大體腔的恐龍之一。<ref name="luetal2007"/>牠與親緣物種[[大夏巨龍|大夏巨龍]]、[[汝陽龍|汝陽龍]]並列為目前發現最大型的[[亞洲|亞洲]]恐龍。<ref>Jinyou Mo, Jincheng Li, Yunchuan Ling, Eric Buffetaut, Suravech Suteethorn Varavud, Suteethorne Haiyan Tong, Gilles Cuny, Romain Amiot & Xing Xu (2020). [https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0195667119303623 New fossil remain of ''Fusuisaurus zhaoi'' (Sauropoda: Titanosauriformes) from the Lower Cretaceous of Guangxi, southern China.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0195667119303623 |date=20200731043126 }} ''Cretaceous Research'': '''104379''' (advance online publication). doi: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cretres.2020.104379 {{Wayback|url=https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cretres.2020.104379 |date=20200401115904 }}</ref>{{link-en|葛瑞格利·保羅|Gregory S. Paul}}在2019年指出汝楊黃河巨龍的背肋長度與[[巴塔哥巨龍屬|巴塔哥巨龍]]相當，而薦骨可能也具有相近的尺寸，估計體重界於45至55噸。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Paul|first=Gregory S.|date=2019|title=Determining the largest known land animal: A critical comparison of differing methods for restoring the volume and mass of extinct animals|url=http://www.gspauldino.com/Titanomass.pdf|journal=Annals of the Carnegie Museum|volume=85 (4)|pages=335-358|via=|access-date=2020-10-03|archive-date=2021-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115134229/http://www.gspauldino.com/Titanomass.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==分類==
